            <title>[LU-3951] OST-object inconsistency self detect and check</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-3951</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;For the RPC from client to OST, if its taken parent FID does not match the information stored in the OST-object, then the OST will query the MDS whether the client given information is correct or not. If not, the client RPC will be denied, otherwise the OST-object will be repaired.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
